    "synopsis": "On the distant world of Caliban, an agent of Rogal Dorn finds himself the prisoner of a legion whose loyalties may be divided. Garviel Loken, on his first mission as a Knight-Errant, has deliberately allowed himself to be captured inside the Dark Angels' fortress of Aldurukh to engineer a face-to-face meeting with Luther, while Iacton Cruze slips deeper into the citadel in search of answers. Shackled and bound, the former Luna Wolf must fight a battle of wits, lest his very presence push another legion into the arms of the Warmaster.",
